    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ATSF is a<strong> </strong>game about <strong>MOVING</strong> and <strong>FIGHTNING</strong> in unique ways, with insane focus in player's expression. Explore this huge world, unlocking new powers to fly around and unveil the secrets behind each core Biome.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Accessible and engaging gameplay, as deep as you want.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lot of enemies, worlds and challenges to put your skills to test.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A complete story to slowly unveil.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COMBINE YOUR ELEMENTS TO DESTROY YOUR ENEMIES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your kit, and combine all your unique elements to release devastating combos. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn to parry, learn to dodge and find your moment to attack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207230/extras/180efe55cada0fca14e0f02fb3b15635.poster.avif?t=1764077772\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207230/extras/180efe55cada0fca14e0f02fb3b15635.webm?t=1764077772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207230/extras/180efe55cada0fca14e0f02fb3b15635.mp4?t=1764077772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UNLOCK ABILITIES TO TRAVERSE THE WORLD</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get more skills to travel and find your own paths, discover secrets, express yourself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207230/extras/7185bef1bcb380c593e332ec7dfbcd5f.poster.avif?t=1764077772\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207230/extras/7185bef1bcb380c593e332ec7dfbcd5f.webm?t=1764077772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207230/extras/7185bef1bcb380c593e332ec7dfbcd5f.mp4?t=1764077772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHALLENGING AND SPECTACULAR BOSSFIGHTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Put your skills to test in the final fights and secret challenges. Use all the learnt skills to defeat the creatures that live in the cores of the worlds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207230/extras/70935445d6fb7b457df0719d6633d4bf.poster.avif?t=1764077772\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207230/extras/70935445d6fb7b457df0719d6633d4bf.webm?t=1764077772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207230/extras/70935445d6fb7b457df0719d6633d4bf.mp4?t=1764077772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE THE SEA OF CLOUDS AND DISCOVER NEW ISLANDS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world is filled with things to do, play minigames, find small islands with tons of resources to power your gear! Map the sea of clouds!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207230/extras/ac5ea6ca7688f534e2b44a83fa8d8951.poster.avif?t=1764077772\" width=1030 height=620 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207230/extras/ac5ea6ca7688f534e2b44a83fa8d8951.webm?t=1764077772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207230/extras/ac5ea6ca7688f534e2b44a83fa8d8951.mp4?t=1764077772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
